headline: Will Chen joins Westfield Specialty as U.S. Chief Financial Officer
summary: Westfield, a U.S.-based property and casualty insurance company, today announces that Will Chen will be joining the company as Westfield Specialty U.S. Chief Financial Officer reporting to Westfield Specialty President Jack Kuhn.
